    <briefdescription>
<para>TCP session to the Tryll server and its supporting value types. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Declares <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client" kindref="compound">Tryll::TryllClient</ref>, the entry point for the C++ client library. The session-level types — <ref refid="_tryll_client_8h_1a9d11d2210bc3e16a2ec7164bcc361bcd" kindref="member">Tryll::Client::ModelStatus</ref>, <ref refid="struct_tryll_1_1_client_1_1_model_info" kindref="compound">Tryll::Client::ModelInfo</ref>, <ref refid="_tryll_client_8h_1a655e81b819f1af79cb6320bec974e14a" kindref="member">Tryll::Client::DownloadProgressCallback</ref> — live in the <computeroutput>Tryll::Client</computeroutput> namespace.</para>
<para>Typical connect-create-use flow:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>client<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_tryll_client_1a6a2ceb8e0a5af81bd91baad797b69d02" kindref="member">Tryll::TryllClient::Connect</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>9100);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">client.ConfigureSession(<ref refid="_graph_description_8h_1ac21687d02192ae842125519cf23f2185a83888cbc1972ac14a87fcbde96092c29" kindref="member">Tryll::Client::InferenceEngine::LlamaCpp</ref>);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>agent<sp/>=<sp/>client.CreateAgent(graph);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">agent.SendText(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;hi&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">agent.Destroy();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">client.Shutdown();</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
